des:
TwinFlame - Daily Horoscopes

Get your daily horoscope delivered right to your Alexa Flash Briefing! This skill provides you with insights into your day ahead, based on your zodiac sign. 

The skill is free to use!

The skill is updated daily, so you always have the latest information!

Features:
- Daily horoscopes for all 12 zodiac signs

How to use:
- Enable the "TwinFlame - Daily Horoscopes" skill in the Alexa app.
- Configure your Flash Briefing to include the horoscope feed for your sign.
- Say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing?"
- Listen to your daily horoscope!

Benefits:
Learn more about your zodiac sign and what the stars have in store for you!
Gain insights into your day ahead so you can make the most of it!
Try it today and see the difference it makes in your life!
